ht-provoking consideration for both academics and general readers.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Mrz 2024) 4aCriminology : Criminology. 4aGender and Sexuality : Gender Studies. 4aGender and Sexuality : Women's Studies. 4aSociology : Sociology of Organization. 4aSociology : Sociology. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Women's Studies.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertSUNY Press eBook Package  Backlist 2000-2013z978311148737340uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978143842632740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781438426327423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781438426327/original  a978-3-11-148737-3  SUNY Press eBook Package  Backlist 2000-2013c2000d2013  aGBV-deGruyter-alles